34唱 1:13 "So now, I will break his yoke bar from upon you, And I will tear off your shackles."
34唱 1:14 The LORD has issued a command concerning you： "Your name will no longer be perpetuated. I will cut off idol and image From the house of your gods. I will prepare your grave, For you are contemptible."
34唱 1:15 Behold, on the mountains the feet of him who brings good news, Who announces peace! Celebrate your feasts, O Judah; Pay your vows. For never again will the wicked one pass through you; He is cut off completely.
34唱 2:1 The one who scatters has come up against you. Man the fortress, watch the road; Strengthen your back, summon all [your] strength.
34唱 2:2 For the LORD will restore the splendor of Jacob Like the splendor of Israel, Even though devastators have devastated them And destroyed their vine branches.
